videos.description: Kansas big man Udoka Azubuike comes up with a big rejection, then uses an up-and-under to finish on the inside.
videos.headline: Azubuike blocks shot, scores on other end

videos.description: Cassius Winston finds a cutting Xavier Tillman, who flies to the rim and flushes down a big finish.
videos.headline: Tillman hammers down one-handed jam

videos.description: Matt McQuaid inbounds the ball to Aaron Henry, who elevates and finishes with an emphatic two-handed stuff.
videos.headline: Henry drives baseline for rim-rocking dunk

videos.description: Aaron Henry tries to finish at the rim, but Udoka Azubuike protects the paint and meets him with a huge rejection.
videos.headline: Azubuike rejects Henry with authority

videos.description: Dedric Lawson and Udoka Azubuike run the pick-and-roll to perfection, leading to a beautiful alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Lawson lobs it up, Azubuike throws it down

videos.description: Devon Dotson gets the outlet pass and blazes down the court, finishing with a crafty layup off the glass.
videos.headline: Dotson shows speed on fast-break layup

videos.description: Kyle Ahrens knocks down a contested 3-pointer as the first-half clock hits zero, cutting the Jayhawks' lead to 50-36 at the break.
videos.headline: Ahrens beats buzzer with 3-ball

videos.description: Kenny Goins swats away Lagerald Vick's layup attempt, and Michigan State converts on the other end with a Joshua Langford triple.
videos.headline: Spartans turn defense into offense with big block

videos.description: Joel Embiid weighs in on the Jayhawks' start to the season, his progress with the Sixers, and Zion Williamson's scouting report.
videos.headline: Embiid on KU basketball: 'It means a lot'

videos.description: Xavier Tillman comes up with a big rejection, and Cassius Winston converts on the other end with a triple plus the foul.
videos.headline: Winston goes for 4-point play

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike continues his dominating night with a drop-step and-1 on Xavier Tillman.
videos.headline: Azubuike powers through contact for and-1

videos.description: Cassius Winston spins into the lane and wills one in after absorbing the contact from Devon Dotson.
videos.headline: Winston spins for and-1

videos.description: Quentin Grimes describes what it was like to suit up for his first college game after knocking down 6 threes and finishing with 21 points.
videos.headline: Grimes after Kansas debut: 'I was super nervous'
